# üöÄ Motion - Minimalist SaaS Landing Page

**Motion** is a modern, responsive landing page designed with a focus on clean typography, soft color palettes, and pure CSS illustrations. This project demonstrates advanced CSS layout techniques and UI design principles without the need for heavy external libraries.



